			<div class="content" id="post-content-4777400">
									

<p>I swear I remember leaving a comment on this one. Well, might as well now.</p>
<p>It really feels against WWS to have taxidermy of some of their animals in their lobby, but then again, I just think taxidermy is a bit weird, plus Tim's dad <em>was</em> a taxidermist, so it only makes sense he's more open to it than me.</p>
<p>One of my favorite things about this chapter is John Schut. He just makes this chapter much more&#8230; dreadful. I'm sure that sense of dread is only worse for Fae. Also, I love Sarah and Feather. Gosh darn amazing side-characters. How do you have so many, they're all so good! +1</p>

							</div>

								
					
